Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.58,0:00:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In the distant memory of Hitoyo Pope,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.33,0:00:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw his silhouette.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.42,0:00:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero, just who exactly are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Care to explain what this building is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.92,0:00:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be Pope's hideout?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.54,0:00:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, Arashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.21,0:00:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's a spaceship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A spaceship?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was once on the ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was one of the immigrants who came to Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,from the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.75,0:00:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No changes in the Kunad Gate yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.08,0:01:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Felling of tiredness is losing yourself♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♫How do you still create a relationship each other♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It’s my awkward friend’s fault♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.25,0:01:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Until death, wanting someone somewhere to embrace me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♫While the devil is not here and between the chaos♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.13,0:01:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Aiming between win and lose♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.46,0:01:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Not to be running out of patience for now\NI’m trying to be careful♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You'll see I'm always on your side♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.25,0:01:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’re frigid and your roller\Ncoaster inside the brain♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The grungy days and the unprecedented catastrophy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Where is the glory buried♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The lonely monster in a moment♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.54,0:02:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The bullet shot by the machinegun goes parallelly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫To pierce with the theory♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The bullet shot by the machinegun goes parallelly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It’s the same today\NTo connect vividly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.96,0:02:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’re frigid and the theory in the brain♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,TWO THOUSAND YEARS OF LONGING
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You came from the Moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the immigrants?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not buying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you're over 2000 years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm actually very old.\NSo show some respect for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it. We've had enough of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.54,0:02:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Kyoka and Arashi should know what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.67,0:02:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a capsule used for cold sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Cold sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Arashi, Kyoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.29,0:02:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not widely used just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's been bothering me since\Nwe came to Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.13,0:03:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This building too. Its structure is unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's totally possible\Nit may be some kind of spaceship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But where are the other members\Nof the immigrants?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, all people in Togetsu\Nare design children.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Only dozens of immigrants survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Like myself, they went into cold sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's normal to be shocked\Nby all this information.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you really lived 2000 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I even knew your ancestor,\Nthe founding father Yakumo Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Soldiers from Togetsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,OSF soldiers! Did Suoh send them here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanabi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-Kyoka!\N-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right. Kyoka is with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm with Luka. Where is Tsugumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm with Kagero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiden and I managed to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, can you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka? Is this telepathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Suoh turned off the psynet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother is looking for a countermeasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But it will take some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The soldiers from Suoh are headed your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, come back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We must go now, Tsugumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane Randall?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Sumeragi was with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They are escaping to the Hieno Mountain\Nas we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Our target is the traitor Lieutenant Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you capture him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we lost them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They are still searching for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a cave five kilometers\Nsouth-west of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can reach the foothill via the passageway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly,\Nthat place is off-limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been that way since I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:06:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, it's a place of danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But the soldiers are still after us.\NWe have no other way out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way out is forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The OSF is not our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to avoid any fighting with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's regroup there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maintain the brain talk connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you knew Yakumo Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That man was the leader of the immigrants.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He was an outstanding leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a cheerful and optimistic person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakumo led the immigrant group "Ark" to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,To enable more people to live here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:07:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,they changed Earth's environment for the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the end, the project was abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.67,0:07:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the terminal data from Togetsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the Extinction Belt appeared\Nwhen the immigrants arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the Extinction Belt the cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I heard,\Nsomething happened to the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Something came from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even Kyoka knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there is a lot to be told here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain what happened 2000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,After we arrived on Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,we established a connection\Nwith our counterpart on the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That was when some sort of mutations occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,People on the Moon started to become monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,People turned into monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. They became Others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, a comet passed by the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The comet was carrying an unknown substance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That unknown substance fell onto the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It was confirmed later on
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that substance turned\Nany living creatures it touched into monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Moon government called it\Nthe Other Particles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, the rebuilding of Earth\Nhad entered the stage of gravity suppression.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,With that technology, we could prevent\Nthe Other Particles from entering Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The Moon government executed a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They pushed the Other Particles\Nto Earth by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what is known as the Extinction Belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They forfeited the immigrants who came to Earth\Njust to save their own skin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. What about the Others?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Extinction Belt was created by humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,where did the Others come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a Moon base near the Extinction Belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was said that is where the creatures' genes\Nwere dispatched.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The genes came into contact with Other Particles\Nand became the Others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, they fall to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,To think they would go that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,According to records, the Moon population\Nwas over-saturated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that was an attempt\Nto reduce the human population.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But that wasn't right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The people on Moon were\Ndoing their best to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And for that reason, I had to stay on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what happened\Nto the Moon afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even know if there are\Nany people left on the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they survived,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the infection would have spread out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you know, can you forgive\Nthose from the Moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I don't understand\Ntheir frustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But all this happened over 2000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We can reach the foothill through this cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The armored car will be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero, you said this passage was dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I hope we can make it out safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt it would be that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is moving underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's massive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we going to lose Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we haven't lost her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it, it was barely scratched.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We should retreat for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That Other has been nesting here\Nfor a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.17,0:12:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The people from Togetsu and I tried\Nto take it down many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But we never defeated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why the place became off-limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider ourselves fortunate that it didn't\Ncame out from the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any routes around that creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,is right on the path to reach the foothill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What if we run faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That creature was surprisingly quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Its ice attack had pretty good range as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we use Luka's brain power?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know what it'll take us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too risky to use teleportation in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This cave is like a labyrinth\Nof the Hieno Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The soldiers will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way forward is to fight that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to find another exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:13:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We might get lost in these complex routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.08,0:13:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see a large open space.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a strange place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A strange place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There is another empty space\Nright beneath it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell how thick the floor is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not very thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanabi, Geman, Shiden, Luka and Tsugumi,\Nstand by for order.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, Kasane, Kagero, Arashi and I\Nwill lure that creature here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's true that you came from the Moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,why are you helping us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say I'm helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more for my own agenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The immigrants abandoned by the Moon\Nstayed on Earth and founded a new country.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the New Himuka with Yakumo Sumeragi\Nin the center of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.54,0:14:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you've got the history lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are people who never\Ngave up on the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Those people founded Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We went into cold sleep\Nand took turns waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We verified the situation on Earth and tried\Nto establish contact with the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But at some point in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,even Togetsu had changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as the Extinction Belt exists,\NI cannot go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even know the Moon\Nhad been attacked by Others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So they thought
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to save their home,\Nthey could just escape from Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and pretend as if everything the immigrants\Nhad done was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Red Strings and the brain power\Nto time travel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to go back in time\Nand erase everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an attempt to correct a wrong world
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and to realize the right future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Togetsu wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.88,0:15:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a little elaborated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.88,0:15:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,To realize this goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Togetsu actually created the Red Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was just a extraordinary that Yuito\Npossesses the same brain power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.08,0:15:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The soldiers from Suoh\Nare approaching the cave entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.96,0:16:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.54,0:16:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we trust what Kagero said?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. There is no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, it doesn't matter\Nif we're with Seiran or Suoh now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If Togetsu got what they wanted,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,our very existence would be wiped away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:16:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't allow that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't accept that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We are all right here fighting for our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be a byroad up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Another 500 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In 300 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In 200 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In 100 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We need another strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No. If I don't do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been alive for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for you to get some rest down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no soldiers nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wataru, notify us if you spot\Nanything suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero, you didn't finish the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You said
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you had your own agenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Togetsu's spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:19:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I infiltrated Suoh for information.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So why would a spy work with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.88,0:19:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was working on ruining Togetsu's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But to mask my true motive,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I pretended to take their orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best that we retreat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like me,\Nthen this is where we part ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't let history be altered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, I still have family on the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not allow anyone to wipe away\Nthe kid's existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero is serious about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so long since I've seen him this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi knows Kagero very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:19:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust you too, Kagero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course, we will end you if you betray us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I have underestimated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But what should we do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Our only option is to stop Togetsu's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But too many are at risk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.71,0:20:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the means to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What if we told the executives\Nof Seiran and Suoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But we are wanted fugitives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No. If they learn about Togetsu's plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,they might realize now is not the time\Nto fight each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Both Suoh and Seiran have learned about\Nthe history of the Moon immigrants.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They should be on the move as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.25,0:20:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, I don't want to be sitting ducks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No one wants to be wiped from existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. Then we should split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, I'm sorry that I tried to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But Chairman Sumeragi,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,your father, didn't die by my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It had been too long since\Nwe fought together. I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the kind of person\Nwho is just bad at lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.25,0:21:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you making fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have a word with the leaders of Suoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.50,0:21:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I will make sure to talk it through\Nwith my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll persuade those in Seiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.58,0:21:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Our goals have finally aligned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.75,0:22:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.79,0:22:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.25,0:22:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.00,0:22:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.46,0:24:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,NAGI'S ATTACK
